data.description: Beautiful energy smart home w/gorgeous views of State Capital. 3 bedrooms w/their own baths + powder room. Open layout, tall ceilings, Bamboo flooring & tile throughout. Gas fireplace. Eco block construction, LED platinum certified, low E windows, energy star SS appliances. New HVAC, New interior paint in main areas (downstairs room to be painted prior to close). Gated, w/private roof top & balcony. Can't beat this location! Perfect home for entertaining. Solar energy home! See agent remarks for more info.
